Second Department,

March, 1952.

(March 3, 1952.) In the Matter of the Appointment of a Member of the Committee on Character and Fitness of Applicants for Admission to the Bar for the Second and Tenth Judicial Districts.

Present — Nolan, P. J., Carswell, Johnston, Adel, Wenzel, MacCrate and Schmidt, JJ.
